    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Objects used for exchange or purchase and having the shape of a weapon or that are weapons or parts of weapons, such as projectile points. Weapons used as currency are known from many historical periods globally.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
